      <h3>WHAT IS <strong style="text-transform: none">DBIx::Class</strong> ?</h3>
      <hr/>
        <p>DBIx::Class (also known as DBIC) is an <strong>extensible</strong> and <strong>flexible</strong> Object/Relational Mapper (ORM) written in Perl. The advantage of using an ORM is to speed development, abstract data and make it pole the database. This allows you to represent your business rules through object orientated design and generate boilerplate code for CRUD operations.</p>
